{"title":"娄山关（外一首）","authors":["李真"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"娄山关（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不到怒目环视的面容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴过血的堑壕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长着高大的青松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锈蚀的弹壳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绽开了玫红色的花朵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号咽、马啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弹丸将树枝纷纷撞落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残甲、白骨、雪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与泥沙拌合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今山崖上飞来对对白鸽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田埂上幸福欢乐地降落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我弯下腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾起锈斑如花的弹壳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗅到了岁月郁积的馨香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻开“四渡赤水”的历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友们又在关前走过……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义·红军墓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"残垒不在了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留着勇士的身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅花骑奋鬃长鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲锋号还有余音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拄杖寻觅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乱丝般的心绪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎从头梳理？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不由己洒下两行泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲开思绪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"披上征衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭栏远眺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨光下山与人尽染绿意。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}